            }
        });


Note, I added an exit condition to your thread so it will actually stop (as is, your thread will keep going). You&#39;d probably want to make the exit condition private and add a setter for cleanliness. Also, I&#39;m using [`join`](http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/Thread.html#join%28long%29) to properly wait for your thread to complete.

